   CBS News September 5, 2017, 7:47 AM

How Starbucks covers pricey in vitro fertilization for even its part-time
employees

     * Share
     * Tweet
     * Reddit
     * Flipboard
     * Email

   Why Starbucks covers pricey IVF (BUTTON)

   IFRAME:
   https://www.cbsnews.com/embed/video/?v=1.9e25db78bee65fb3ceea76901207f3
   d59a238e86#1VcLj9u4Ef4rhIAWLWDa1NsycCg2ySbda5LurZMLmjgwKHJkMZZEnUj5kWD%
   2Fe4fya%2FNCr71rge5iJYoczvubmf3k8d7qtuJ7b2a7HkbeRknQ3uyTpyzUxpu9%2B%2BT
   ZfQvezNto6Y08JXGZRTnjMmE0S4qcRpD7lKcioAWkuS8Dv4jyHGnrdncHxY278ein9fznj%
   2FObtv%2FlztxFTO%2FefvhxHbEXb%2F%2Be%2FhRMnx2oB9LpmzJ9dp3cwY%2FXb3HbVP0
